divergence: Divergence?
  lateral: controlled creativity within reasonable bounds
  wild: no idea too strange, explore the full space
  constrained: creative within explicit constraints, find novel combinations
constraint_treatment: Constraint treatment?
  respect: work within all stated constraints
  challenge: question each constraint, suggest removing limiting ones
  ignore-then-reconcile: generate ideas ignoring constraints, then adapt the best
output_count: Output count?
  3: three approaches minimum
  5: five approaches minimum
  exhaustive: generate until the well runs dry
